{
    "json_version": 0x2,
    "name": "EVENT_MESSAGE_QC09_ERN_020.ebm",
    "nb_messages": 0x19,
    "messages": [
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x0,
            "name_id": 0x0,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x0,
            "msg_string": "Oh, Ernie!<CR>Hello!"
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x9,
            "name_id": 0x9,
            "extra_id": 0x122,
            "expr_id": 0x4,
            "msg_id": 0x1,
            "msg_string": "Wow. I'm still not used to seeing you outside your workshop."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x9,
            "name_id": 0x9,
            "extra_id": 0x126,
            "expr_id": 0x2,
            "msg_id": 0x2,
            "msg_string": "But, I'm still worried... Are you okay?"
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x0,
            "name_id": 0x0,
            "extra_id": 0x76,
            "expr_id": 0x3,
            "msg_id": 0x3,
            "msg_string": "I'm fine. I've gotten used to traveling!"
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x9,
            "name_id": 0x9,
            "extra_id": 0x128,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x4,
            "msg_string": "That's when traveling's the most dangerous. There are a lot of things you can't predict in the hills and fields."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x0,
            "name_id": 0x0,
            "extra_id": 0x78,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x5,
            "msg_string": "Really? Like what?"
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x9,
            "name_id": 0x9,
            "extra_id": 0x1,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x6,
            "msg_string": "First, there's always the possibility of running into a vicious animal, or you might even get lost."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x9,
            "name_id": 0x9,
            "extra_id": 0x2,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x7,
            "msg_string": "I mean, there are times when you'll have to make your own path, right?"
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x9,
            "name_id": 0x9,
            "extra_id": 0x7,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x8,
            "msg_string": "And I'm sure there'll be other problems, too. Even I've ran low on drinking water, and fell off a cliff..."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x0,
            "name_id": 0x0,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x9,
            "msg_string": "Ernie, it sounds like you've gone through a lot..."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x9,
            "name_id": 0x9,
            "extra_id": 0x3,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0xa,
            "msg_string": "I've been doing this job for a while. I've experienced just about any kind of danger you can think of."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x9,
            "name_id": 0x9,
            "extra_id": 0x15a,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0xb,
            "msg_string": "Even if you're traveling along a main road, it can still be dangerous."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x9,
            "name_id": 0x9,
            "extra_id": 0x15b,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0xc,
            "msg_string": "So you should walk with travelers or merchants, or hire a bodyguard, okay?"
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x0,
            "name_id": 0x0,
            "extra_id": 0x193,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0xd,
            "msg_string": "Okay. I'll keep that in mind."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x9,
            "name_id": 0x9,
            "extra_id": 0x15d,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0xe,
            "msg_string": "Also, don't rush yourself. It's important to walk at a consistent pace every day."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x9,
            "name_id": 0x9,
            "extra_id": 0x15f,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0xf,
            "msg_string": "If you push yourself too hard and hurt yourself, you'll be in big trouble."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x9,
            "name_id": 0x9,
            "extra_id": 0x15f,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x10,
            "msg_string": "Also, when you're going to sleep, make sure you keep the fire going. It's important to keep the heat and..."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x0,
            "name_id": 0x0,
            "extra_id": 0x34,
            "expr_id": 0x2,
            "msg_id": 0x11,
            "msg_string": "Hehehe, Ernie, you're always worried about me."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x0,
            "name_id": 0x0,
            "extra_id": 0x35,
            "expr_id": 0x2,
            "msg_id": 0x12,
            "msg_string": "You're like a mother...<CR>It makes me happy."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x9,
            "name_id": 0x9,
            "extra_id": 0x161,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x13,
            "msg_string": "I mean, I've known you since you were little... In any case, I'd prefer if you said father..."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x0,
            "name_id": 0x0,
            "extra_id": 0x36,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x14,
            "msg_string": "Hmm...but you feel more like a mother."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x0,
            "name_id": 0x0,
            "extra_id": 0x1,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x15,
            "msg_string": "I'm sure that a mother would be as kind as you, Ernie."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x9,
            "name_id": 0x9,
            "extra_id": 0x15c,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x16,
            "msg_string": "Hmm, I can't really agree, but..."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x9,
            "name_id": 0x9,
            "extra_id": 0x5,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x17,
            "msg_string": "Okay, I'm fine with being a mother, but in return, make sure you do what your mother tells you!"
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x0,
            "name_id": 0x0,
            "extra_id": 0x195,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x18,
            "msg_string": "Okay, will do. Thank you for caring about me, Ernie!"
        }
    ]
}